title: Mobile Phone Manager - SonicHANDY v9.3 (Complete-With extras)
description:
SonicHANDY lets you operate a mobile phone through a PC and organize your messages, contacts, calls, etc. more easily. It is intended primarily for Sony Ericsson phones, but other mobiles can also be used.

More info at <a href=" http://www.sonichandy.com" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.sonichandy.com</a>

v9.3
